In re MOSHER, Justice of the Peace. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fourth Department. February 15, 1894.) In the matter of the application for the removal of Lewis E. Mosher, a justice of the peace in and for the town of Horseheads, N. Y.

Argued before'HARDIN, P. J., and MARTIN and MERWIN, JJ.

■ Proceeding dismissed. Per- curiam memorandum filed with the clerk of Broome county. See 24 N. Y. Supp. 1147; 26 N. Y. Supp. 1127.
